<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; }
        .container { width: 90%; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; }
        h2 { color: #0073e6; }
        p { font-size: 16px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hi <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</h2>
        <p>We hope you're doing well! Just a reminder that your subscription started on <b><%= startDate %></b></p>
        <p>We wanted to inform you that there will be a price increase starting the following year 2026. Please ensure your payment details are up to date to continue enjoying our services without interruption.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this change, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing us!</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p><b>EaseTruck</b></p>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>
